      <guid>https://gunn.kim/talk/2020-09-corona-book-publish/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote class=&#34;twitter-tweet&#34;&gt;&lt;p lang=&#34;ko&#34; dir=&#34;ltr&#34;&gt;코로나 0년 초회복의 시작 - 이원재, 최영준 외 &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/wbp1qansk2&#34;&gt;https://t.co/wbp1qansk2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; 어크로스의 문장들 (@acrossbook) &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/acrossbook/status/1301790484998750208?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;September 4, 2020&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
